  caller_name: Greg
  caller_dialogue: "Hello, my daughter told me to call this number when I told her
    about a tall man with red eyes looking at me through my window for weeks on end.
    Told her not to worry, it might just be my old eyes failing me\u2026but she looked
    really spooked out, so I decided to give in and call y'all."
